# --- OS / editor cruft ---
.DS_Store
**/.DS_Store
~$*
*.swp
.idea/
.vscode/

# IMPORTANT: this scaffold SHIPS the .claude/ folder — it is the payload.
# Do NOT add `.claude/` to this file. (Most real projects gitignore .claude;
# this repo is the exception because distributing it is the whole point.)

# --- Below: patterns you will likely want in the TARGET project,
#     not in this scaffold. Uncomment per project as needed. ---
#
# # Nextflow
# .nextflow/
# .nextflow.log*
# work/
# trace.txt
# report.html
#
# # Python
# __pycache__/
# *.pyc
# .venv/
#
# # R
# .Rhistory
# renv/library/
#
# # Large / regenerable scientific artifacts (keep small text summaries)
# **/output/**
# !**/output/**/
# !**/output/**/README.md
# !**/output/**/REPORT.md
# !**/output/**/*.md
